sequenceDiagram
  participant Android as Android CodexViewModel
  participant GW as terminalGateway.js
  participant Feed as CodexIpcFeed
  participant IPC as CodexIpcClient
  participant Owner as Desktop / VS Code owner

  Android->>GW: set_active_conversation
  GW-->>Android: conversation_surface_snapshot
  GW-->>Android: follower_mode_changed

  Android->>GW: set_active_follower_mode(true)
  GW-->>Android: follower_mode_changed(enabled=true)

  Android->>GW: follower_send_message
  GW->>GW: check IPC online / active allowed / follower mode / status
  GW->>Feed: sendRequest(thread-follower-start-turn)
  Feed->>IPC: IPC request envelope
  IPC->>Owner: thread-follower-start-turn
  Owner-->>IPC: response
  IPC-->>Feed: ack/error
  Feed-->>GW: result
  GW-->>Android: follower_message_sent

  Owner-->>IPC: updated thread-stream-state-changed
  IPC-->>Feed: broadcast
  Feed-->>GW: new surface
  GW-->>Android: conversation_surface_snapshot